NOTE: We do not have enough variety of systems to test all configurations, so if you face issues, please consider dropping an email at adrian.game.3d@gmail.com . We do this just as a hobby on the side, so kindly do not mind if there is a delay in response.

Linux:
======
- To compile the game, you need to have the following dependencies installed

SDL_image
SDL_ttf
SDL_mixer
SDL_sound

	On Fedora, just run this to download and install the dependencies

	yum install SDL_image SDL_ttf SDL_sound SDL_mixer

- Enter make in the src directory to build the executable - adrian


